Class Entrant

java.lang.Object
com.example.syntaxeventlottery.User
com.example.syntaxeventlottery.Entrant
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Entrant extends User implements Serializable
Represents an Entrant in the Event Lottery System. Extends the User class to include entrant-specific functionalities.
